name: Nonneg.bot_eq
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝ : Preorder α
a : α
⊢ Eq Bot.bot ⟨a, ⋯⟩
decl:
theorem bot_eq [Preorder α] {a : α} : (⊥ : { x : α // a ≤ x }) = ⟨a, le_rfl⟩ :=
  rfl

name: Nonneg.noMaxOrder
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝¹ : PartialOrder α
inst✝ : NoMaxOrder α
a : α
⊢ NoMaxOrder (Subtype fun x => LE.le a x)
decl:
instance noMaxOrder [PartialOrder α] [NoMaxOrder α] {a : α} : NoMaxOrder { x : α // a ≤ x } :=
  show NoMaxOrder (Ici a) by infer_instance

name: Nonneg.instDenselyOrdered
initialProofState:
α : Type u_1
inst✝¹ : Preorder α
inst✝ : DenselyOrdered α
a : α
⊢ DenselyOrdered (Subtype fun x => LE.le a x)
decl:
instance instDenselyOrdered [Preorder α] [DenselyOrdered α] {a : α} :
    DenselyOrdered { x : α // a ≤ x } :=
  show DenselyOrdered (Ici a) from Set.instDenselyOrdered
